import HeaderLink from '../HeaderLink'
import style from './header.module.css'

export default function Header() {
    return (

        <header className={style.header}>
            <nav>
                H
            </nav>
            <HeaderLink url="./">
                Home
            </HeaderLink>
            <HeaderLink url="./cadastromenu">
                Cadastro Menu
            </HeaderLink>
        </header>

    )
}
